<td>Twin</td>
<td>&pound;200 - &pound;300</td>
<td>Compact, modern design with a space under the bed for a desk or play area. Suitable for small spaces.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Zinus Talia Twin-Over-Full</td>
